instance_methods.doc:
Fetch *key* or set it to *value*.

```
h = {"foo" => "bar"}
h.fetch_or_set("foo", "baz"); pp h
# {"foo" => "bar"}
h.fetch_or_set("bar", "baz"); pp h
# {"foo" => "bar", "bar" => "baz"}
```

